			Profile
			
			BriefIntroductionofProfessorZhuBaiming
ZhuBaiming,bornin1964,Shangyu,ZhejiangProvince,hasbeenawardedaBachelor&rsquo;sDegreeandaMaster&rsquo;sDegreeinHangzhouuniversity(NowmergedintoZhejiangUniversity)andXiamenuniversityrespectively.HismainresearchareasareTheoryofPublicFinanceandFiscalSystemandPolicy.HeisnowtheProfessorandMAstudentadviseratCollegeofEconomics,ZhejiangUniversity,thedirectorofPublicEconomicsandFinancialResearchInstituteofZhejiangUniversity,andtheDepartmentHeadofPublicfinance.Atthesametime,heisalsotheMemberofNationalUniversityFinanceEducationResearchinstitution,vicedirectorofEducationSteeringCommitteeofZhejiangprovinceandExecutivememberofZhejiangInstituteofFinance.
ProfessorZhuhaspublishedmanyacademicbooks,suchas《TheComparativeResearchonpublicfinancebetweenchinaandKorea》、《CasesofPublicfinance》and《PublicfinanceinTheoryandpractice》.Healsopublished90academicpapersintotalon《FinanceandTradeEconomics》、《TheEconomist》,etc.HisRepresentativepapersare:《TheObjectivesandApproachesonFiscalExpenditure&rsquo;sStructureAdjustment》(1992),《NationalDebtBurdenofChina：EmpiricalAnalysisandTrendForecast》(1993),《TheDeviationandCoordinationbetweenNewTaxsystemandTaxDistributionSystem》(1994),《TheIdeaofStandardizationManagementofFinancialCompensationFunds》(1996),《TheConnotationandGeneralityofFinancialFunction》(1997),《TheideaofEstablishingsocialsecuritybudget》(1998),《TheChoicesofCorporateIncomeTaxRateafterCombination》(1998),《Scientificallydefinethescopeofthecentralandlocalpowers》(1998),《HowtoUnderstand&quot;ConsumptionFinance&quot;》(1999),《theRevolutionofChinaPublicFinance》(2000),《HowtoControlBondScale》(2002),《NewTaxesshouldbeReleasedCarefully》(2002),《AnalyzeRuralTaxReformfromthePerspectiveofPublicFinance》(2002),《SustainabilityofRuralTaxReform》(2003),《AnewideaofSectorBudgetReform》(2005),《SeveralConsiderationsonthe&quot;ProvinceGoverningCounty&quot;FinanceSystem》(2006),《WhatExpenditureReformLacksinpast10years？》(2008),《AnalysisofEqualizationofBasicPublicServicesFromthePerspectiveofCost-effective》(2008),《EstablishmentofBudgetcontrolsystemofForwardErrorCorrection(FEC)andBackwardErrorCorrection(BEC)》(2010).
Heholdsmorethan10MinisterialandProvincialIssues,asfollowing:DevelopmentalModelofPublicFinance(2000SocialScienceFundProjectinZhejiangprovince),《studyonTreasuryCentralizedcollectionandpayment》（2002socialcouncilkeyissueinZhejiangprovince）《studyonAgriculturaltaxtoSocialSecuritytaxoffarmers》（2003SocialScienceFundProjectinZhejiang&nbsp;province）Centralshareofadministrativefeesmanagement(2004issueofSuperviseOfficeoftheMinistryofFinance)RealEstateDevelopmentandPublicPolicy(issuesofConstructionDepartmentinZhejiangprovince)CompulsoryEducationandLocalpublicfinancestudies(2005national&nbsp;ScienceFundProject)studyon&quot;ProvinceGoverningCounty&quot;FinanceSystem(2006SocialScienceFundProjectinZhejiang&nbsp;province),PublicPolicyResearchofPromotingTechnologyInnovation(issuesofScienceandTechnologyDepartmentinZhejiangprovince)studyonEqualizationofbasicpublicservices(issueofZhejiangInstituteofFinance)&quot;Trinity&quot;ofthefinancialoperationmode(issuesofDepartmentofFinanceinZhejiangprovince)
Hewasawardedthe&ldquo;BaosteelExcellentTeacher&rdquo;and&ldquo;NationalExcellentMPAProffesor&rdquo;issuedbyMinistryofEducation,&ldquo;ExcellentandPopularProfessorofZhejiangUniversity.HiscourseofPublicFinancewasawardedtheprizefortheprovinciallevelexcellentundergraduatecourseinZhejiangProvince.Intheyear2001and2007,hewasvotedtwiceasoneof&ldquo;MyfavoriteteacherinZhejiangUniversity&rdquo;byZJUstudents.HehasvisitedKanagawaUniversity(Japan)andTamkangUniversity(Taiwan)foracademicexchanges.HehasreceiveddozensofinterviewsbymedialikeChinaNewsWeekly,SouthernWeekend,ZhejiangSatelliteTV,etc.Heisofteninvitedtogivethemereportsandacademiclecturesonpubliceconomicissuestogovernmentdepartmentsandcolleges.
			
				
